এই মন মাতানো Bangla folk fusion Song-এ অসাধারণ কণ্ঠে হাজির Onamika Orin, 
Song: Mr. Kailla

Lyrics | Tune | Music: Hassan Yahea
Producer: Hassan Yahea
Label: Chitro Bangla
Cast:   Khan Rosne, Najim Ahmed, Jannat Jahan, Mukul Jamil,
Mehedi Hasan Rony

“Shohag” marks a return to Tanishk Bagchi’s Bengali roots, blending Bangla emotional sensibility with globally inspired rhythms in a way that resonates beyond borders. Joining him is KikiMoteleba, whose Afrobeat hit Tigini found international traction, adding a distinct pulse to this cross-cultural sound.
